3#!#2023-06-16 09:30:00.0000000#!#Morning Break
4#!#2023-06-16 12:00:00.0000000#!#Noon
5#!#2023-06-16 13:30:00.0000000#!#Afternoon Break
6#!#2023-06-16 15:45:30.1234570#!#Late Afternoon
7#!#2023-06-16 17:30:00.0000000#!#End of Day
8#!#2023-06-16 18:15:00.0000000#!#Evening
9#!#2023-06-16 20:00:00.0000000#!#Night
